            <title><![CDATA[关于做好近期实验室安全工作的提示]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[关于做好近期实验室安全工作的提示]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/06/05/122356</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/06/05/122356</guid>
