            <title><![CDATA[关于电机楼广场交通管制的通知]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[关于电机楼广场交通管制的通知]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/06/05/122345</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/06/05/122345</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Jun 2025 09:53:05 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;word-break:break-all&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;“在贺信精神引领下”纪念建校&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;105&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;周年主题升旗仪式将于&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;2025&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;日在一校区电机楼广场举行。为确保升旗仪式活动顺利进行，学校决定&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;日&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;6:30&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;—&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;9:00&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;对电机楼广场区域实施交通管制，具体如下：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;word-break:break-all&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;一、交通管制期间电机楼广场区域禁止车辆通行。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;word-break:break-all&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;二、去往东部区域车辆从正门弧形通道绕行（临时双向通行，活动后恢复单行）；去往西部区域车辆可从电机楼门前甬道、正门弧形通道绕行。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;word-break:break-all&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;三、请广大师生积极支持配合，确保升旗仪式活动安全顺利。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;word-break:break-all&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;望周知，给您带来不便敬请谅解。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:293.9pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;word-break:break-all&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;保卫处&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:293.9pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;word-break:break-all&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;学生工作部（处）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;团委&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:293.9pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;word-break:break-all&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;2025&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background:white&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;日&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;image-20250605141149-1&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;bb3e2db5-1bb2-4e9c-9d07-2a3547efdaf5&quot; height=&quot;724&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/%5Bdate%3Acustom%3AY%5D/%5Bdate%3Acustom%3Am%5D/%5Bdate%3Acustom%3Ad%5D/image-20250605141149-1.jpeg&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded>
        </item>
